    <h1>ðŸ“Š Dragon Ball Legends Tier Maker</h1>
    <h2 class="meta-subtitle">
        âš¡ TIER LIST MAKER PARA {TextRarity[rarPath as keyof typeof TextRarity].toUpperCase()}
        <span class="rising-rush-badge"></span>
    </h2>
    <p class="highlight">
        Â¡Crea y comparte tu Tier List personalizada de personajes {TextRarity[rarPath as keyof typeof TextRarity]}!<br />
    </p>

    <h3>ðŸš€ Explorar otras categorÃ­as</h3>

    <section class="tiermaker-list">
        <a href="/tiermaker/he" class={`${rarPath == "he" ? "selected" : ""}`}>Hero</a>
        <a href="/tiermaker/ex" class={`${rarPath == "ex" ? "selected" : ""}`}>Extreme</a>
